        protected abstract boolean indexOfAfterCheck(Geometry input,

        Checks that the point computed by indexOfAfter is the same as the input point. (This should be the case for all except pathological cases, such as the input test point being beyond the end of the line).
        Parameters:
        input -
        testPt -
        Returns:
        true if the result of indexOfAfter is the same as the input point
